    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Conduit \u2014 Platform 1 \u00b7 Health & Experience\n**Is it working, fast, and good?** The **top strip** is the 5-second read \u2014 green good, amber watch, red act. The rows below detail traffic, latency, intent routing and how requests resolved. Infrastructure internals live on **Platform 2**; cost & eval live in Insights (Langfuse)."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Request success rate",
      "description": "Share of requests handled correctly (ANSWERED + deliberate CLARIFIED/DENIED) over all outcomes, 1h. Clarifying an ambiguous ask and denying out-of-coverage access are correct behaviors, not failures \u2014 only genuinely FAILED/errored requests lower this. Good ~100%.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 4,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "red",
                "value": null
              },
              {
                "color": "yellow",
                "value": 95
              },
              {
                "color": "green",
                "value": 99
              }
            ]
          },
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "prometheus"
          },
          "expr": "100 * sum(increase(conduit_request_outcome_total{outcome=~\"ANSWERED|CLARIFIED|DENIED\"}[1h])) / clamp_min(sum(increase(conduit_request_outcome_total[1h])),1)",
          "legendFormat": "success",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ]
        },
        "showThresholdLabels": false,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
